What ſhall 8083, the firſt Man's part give? Anſwer 31 Chains 52 Links;
which ſet off from A to F, and drawing the Line FB, you divide the Trapezia as deſired; the Triangle ABF being the Firſt Man's Portion, and the Trapezia BCFD, the ſecond's.
